description: Load remogram SDLC lane skills for topo/ and Plan Lane work on private Gitea remo (maintainer dogfood only).
alwaysApply: true
---

For **`topo/**`** or **lane work** in this private dogfood checkout:

1. Load **`remogram-sdlc-core`**, then the lane skill (e.g. **`remogram-plan-lane`**).
2. Load **`remogram-dogfood`** for Gitea forge setup and review/merge proof rules.
3. Load **`remogram-core`** when also editing `packages/**`.

**Do not load** generic `topogram-*-lane` or `topogram-core` during the lane-skills experiment.

Integration branch: **`remo`**. Planning: **`goal/*` only** for `topo/` commits. Forge: **`remogram`** CLI/MCP.

Install: `./scripts/install-agent-skills.sh --cursor --dogfood`

This rule is stripped on public export.
